{"type":"message","id":"10d816ec","parentId":"902c6b86","timestamp":"2026-04-10T01:43:43.573Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The miaoda_coding task has been completed. The page is ready with:\n- Deep blue tech-style interface\n- Four phase cards with 28 checkable tasks\n- Real-time progress bar\n- Data automatically saved in browser localStorage\n\nLet me summarize what was accomplished.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"博士申请进度追踪网页已创建完成。\n\n**功能亮点：**\n- 🎯 **四个申请阶段**：打基础 → 积累素材 → 陶瓷申请 → 等待入学\n- ✅ **28项可勾选任务**：覆盖英语备考、整理简历、找推荐人、写研究计划、陶瓷套磁等\n- 📊 **实时进度条**：直观显示整体完成度\n- 💾 **localStorage 本地持久化**：关闭浏览器后数据不丢失\n- 🎨 **深蓝科技感配色**：蓝色系，清晰专业\n- 📱 **响应式布局**：手机和电脑都能流畅使用\n\n---\n\n🦞 祝 yuriy 博士申请顺利！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":485,"output":201,"cacheRead":30907,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31593,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775785416955}}
